{"tid":559411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔巴士車禍應由「佔中」查起","createTime":"2018-02-13T07:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T07:04:59.000Z","uid":31278,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8ebe70e521f2400095243d21559867a456ddd1","tid":559411,"uid":31278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T07:04:59.000Z","msg":"專欄作家屈穎妍於《頭條日報》專欄談及大埔巴士19死奪命車禍，稱應由2014年的「佔中」查起。<br />\n <br />\n專欄題為＜金鐘的蝴蝶與大埔的龍捲風＞，屈穎妍提及「蝴蝶效應」，認為由法官領導的獨立調查委員會，應由2014年「風馬牛不相及的佔中事件」查起。<br />\n<br />\n她解釋，「佔中」打開了「潘多拉盒子」，釋放了人的獸性、罪惡心，「自從那年開始，香港原本的投訴文化變本加厲，人們一不如意，就兇人、罵人、影你相、撩交打，以人權、私隱、公義為藉口作惡，罵人打人」。<br />\n<br />\n屈穎妍形容「佔中」是「拍翼蝴蝶」，大埔車禍就是「龍捲風」，「於是，遲開車的司機，受千夫所指；忍無可忍的車長，以油門和軚盤報復，最後，兩敗俱傷」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180213/s00001/1518499504734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180213%2Fs00001%2F1518499504734&d=hJwxMhAxtaGs%2B0tgGmBkLcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2fa72160\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180213%2Fs00001%2F1518499504734&h=ca7e57d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180213/s00001/1518499504734</a><br />\n<br />\n肯定係佔中嚇到佢變左弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佔中可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}